headline.print_headline: 'Scandal' Season Ender a TV Ratings Winner for ABC
headline.main: 'Scandal' Season Ender a TV Ratings Winner for ABC

lead_paragraph: ABC's explosive season-ending episode of "Scandal" was seen by 10.6 million viewers last week, the biggest audience ever for the drama.
